  "sn22.148": "One gone forth should dwell contemplating suffering in the aggregates.",
  "sn22.149": "One gone forth should dwell contemplating not-self in the aggregates.",
  "sn22.150": "Pleasure and pain arise inside oneself due to grasping the aggregates.",
