  "sn30.1": "Phoenixes may be born from eggs, the womb, moisture, or spontaneously.",
  "sn30.2":
    "Phoenixes may be born from eggs, the womb, moisture, or spontaneously. Each of them may carry off a dragon of lower birth.",
  "sn30.3": "One becomes an egg born phoenix due to ambivalent deeds in a past life and the appropriate aspiration.",
