  "sn31.1": "Fairies may live in fragrant roots and other vegetation.",
  "sn31.2": "Someone of good conduct and appropriate aspiration may be reborn as a fairy.",
  "sn31.3":
    "Someone of good conduct and appropriate aspiration may be reborn as a fairy living in fragrant roots if they give fragrant roots.",
  "sn31.4-12":
    "Someone of good conduct and appropriate aspiration may be reborn as a fairy living in various kinds of vegetation if they give the gift of that kind of vegetation.",
  "sn31.13-22":
    "Someone of good conduct and appropriate aspiration may be reborn as a fairy living in fragrant roots if they give various gifts.",
  "sn31.23-112":
    "Someone of good conduct and appropriate aspiration may be reborn as a fairy living in various kinds of vegetation if they give various gifts",
  "sn32.1": "Cloud gods may live in cool clouds, warm clouds, storm clouds, wind clouds, or rain clouds.",
  "sn32.2": "Someone of good conduct and appropriate aspiration may be reborn as a cloud god.",
  "sn32.3-12":
    "Someone of good conduct and appropriate aspiration may be reborn as a cloud god in a cool cloud if they give various gifts.",
  "sn32.13-52":
    "Someone of good conduct and appropriate aspiration may be reborn as a cloud god living in various kinds of cloud if they give various gifts.",
  "sn32.53": "When the cool cloud gods decide to revel in their own element, the weather becomes cool.",
  "sn32.54": "When the warm cloud gods decide to revel in their own element, the weather becomes warm.",
  "sn32.55": "When the storm cloud gods decide to revel in their own element, the weather becomes stormy.",
  "sn32.56": "When the wind cloud gods decide to revel in their own element, the weather becomes windy.",
  "sn32.57": "When the rain cloud gods decide to revel in their own element, the weather becomes rainy",
